NO NORTH · NON — the capstone: "outside" smuggled a privileged origin the field never gave. Move the origin and the dark moves with it; the field can't self-derive one (node-verified). So the frame must come from an external chooser — the first author. There is no north in the field; you are it. Catch credited to David (ROOT0)…
